61const char* Scte128_tag (int8u tag)
62{
63 switch (tag)
64 {
65 case 0x00: return "Forbidden";
66 case 0x01: return "Used by DVB";
67 case 0x02: return "AU_Information";
68 case 0xDF: return "Registered";
69 case 0xFF: return "Reserved";
70 default : return tag<0xE0?"Reserved":"User private";
71 }
72}

114{
115 0,
116 3,
117 4,
118 5,
119 6,
120 7,
121 8,
122 6,
123 7,
124};
125
126const int8u MpegTs_DtsNeural_Channels_6[MpegTs_DtsNeural_6_Count]=
127{
128 0,
129 6,
130 7,
131 8,
132};
133
134const int8u MpegTs_DtsNeural_Channels(int8u Channels, int8u config_id)
135{
136 if (config_id==0)
137 return 0;
138
139 switch (Channels)
140 {
141 case 2 :
142 if (config_id>=MpegTs_DtsNeural_2_Count)
143 return 0;
144 return MpegTs_DtsNeural_Channels_2[config_id];
145 case 6 :
146 if (config_id>=MpegTs_DtsNeural_6_Count)
147 return 0;
148 return MpegTs_DtsNeural_Channels_6[config_id];
149 default: return 0;
150 }
151}

233//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
234Ztring Decimal_Hexa(int64u Number)
235{
236 Ztring Temp;
237 Temp.From_Number(Number);
238 Temp+=__T(" (0x");
239 Temp+=Ztring::ToZtring(Number, 16);
240 Temp+=__T(")");
241 return Temp;
242}

252#endif //MEDIAINFO_DUPLICATE

254 //Configuration

256 #if MEDIAINFO_EVENTS

259 #endif //MEDIAINFO_EVENTS

262 #endif //MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
263 MustSynchronize=true;
264 Buffer_TotalBytes_FirstSynched_Max=64*1024;
265 Buffer_TotalBytes_Fill_Max=(int64u)-1; //Disabling this feature for this format, this is done in the parser
266 Trusted_Multiplier=2;
267 #if MEDIAINFO_DEMUX

269 #endif //MEDIAINFO_DEMUX

273 BDAV_Size=0; //No BDAV header
274 #endif
275 #if defined(MEDIAINFO_TSP_YES)

278 #ifdef MEDIAINFO_ARIBSTDB24B37_YES
279 FromAribStdB24B37=false;
280 #endif
281
282 //Data
283 MpegTs_JumpTo_Begin=MediaInfoLib::Config.MpegTs_MaximumOffset_Get();
284 MpegTs_JumpTo_End=MediaInfoLib::Config.MpegTs_MaximumOffset_Get()/4;
285 MpegTs_ScanUpTo=(int64u)-1;
286 Searching_TimeStamp_Start=true;
287 Complete_Stream=NULL;
288 Begin_MaxDuration=MediaInfoLib::Config.ParseSpeed_Get()>=0.8?(int64u)-1:MediaInfoLib::Config.MpegTs_MaximumScanDuration_Get()*27/1000;
289 ForceStreamDisplay=MediaInfoLib::Config.MpegTs_ForceStreamDisplay_Get();
290
291 #if MEDIAINFO_SEEK
292 Seek_Value=(int64u)-1;
293 Seek_ID=(int64u)-1;
294 InfiniteLoop_Detect=0;
295 Duration_Detected=false;
296 #endif //MEDIAINFO_SEEK

308//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
309void File_MpegTs::Streams_Accept()
310{
311 Fill(Stream_General, 0, General_Format, BDAV_Size?"BDAV":(TSP_Size?"MPEG-TS 188+16":"MPEG-TS"), Unlimited, true, true);
312
313 #if MEDIAINFO_DEMUX && MEDIAINFO_NEXTPACKET
314 if (Config->NextPacket_Get() && Config->Event_CallBackFunction_IsSet())
315 Config->Demux_EventWasSent=true;
316 #endif //MEDIAINFO_DEMUX && MEDIAINFO_NEXTPACKET
317
318 if (!IsSub)
319 {
320 #if MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED
321 // TODO: temporary disabling theses options for MPEG-TS, because it does not work as expected
322 if (Config->File_IgnoreSequenceFileSize_Get())
323 Config->File_IgnoreSequenceFileSize_Set(false);
324 if (Config->File_IgnoreSequenceFilesCount_Get())
325 Config->File_IgnoreSequenceFilesCount_Set(false);
326 #endif //MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED
327
328 TestContinuousFileNames(24, Ztring(), true);
329 }
330}

332//---------------------------------------------------------------------------

335 Status[User_20]=true;
336}

338//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
339void File_MpegTs::Streams_Update()
340{
341 if (Status[User_19])
342 Streams_Update_Programs();
343
344 if (Status[User_18])
345 Streams_Update_EPG();
346
347 #ifdef MEDIAINFO_MPEGTS_PCR_YES
348 if (Status[User_16])
349 Streams_Update_Duration_Update();
350 #endif //MEDIAINFO_MPEGTS_PCR_YES
351
352 if (Status[User_17])
353 Streams_Update_Duration_End();
354
355 if (File_Name.empty() && Config->ParseSpeed>=1.0)
356 Fill(Stream_General, 0, General_FileSize, (File_Offset+Buffer_Offset!=File_Size)?Buffer_TotalBytes:File_Size, 10, true);
357}
358
359//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
360void File_MpegTs::Streams_Update_Programs()
361{
362 //Per stream
363 bool PerStream_AlwaysParse=ForceStreamDisplay;
364 if (!PerStream_AlwaysParse)
365 {
366 size_t Programs_Size=Complete_Stream->Transport_Streams[Complete_Stream->transport_stream_id].Programs.size();
367 PerStream_AlwaysParse=true;
368 if (Programs_Size<=2)
369 {
370 //Testing if it is a Blu-ray
371 for (complete_stream::transport_stream::programs::iterator Program=Complete_Stream->Transport_Streams[Complete_Stream->transport_stream_id].Programs.begin(); Program!=Complete_Stream->Transport_Streams[Complete_Stream->transport_stream_id].Programs.end(); ++Program)
372 if (Program->first!=0x0000 && Program->second.registration_format_identifier!=Elements::HDMV)
373 {
374 PerStream_AlwaysParse=false;
375 break;
376 }
377 }
378 }
379 for (std::set<int16u>::iterator StreamID=Complete_Stream->PES_PIDs.begin(); StreamID!=Complete_Stream->PES_PIDs.end(); ++StreamID)
380 if (PerStream_AlwaysParse || Complete_Stream->Streams[*StreamID]->IsUpdated_IsRegistered || Complete_Stream->Streams[*StreamID]->IsUpdated_Info)
381 {
382 Streams_Update_Programs_PerStream(*StreamID);
383 Complete_Stream->Streams[*StreamID]->IsUpdated_IsRegistered=false;
384 Complete_Stream->Streams[*StreamID]->IsUpdated_Info=false;
385 }
386
387 //Fill General
388 if (Complete_Stream->transport_stream_id_IsValid)
389 {
390 Fill(Stream_General, 0, General_ID, Complete_Stream->transport_stream_id, 10, true);
391 Fill(Stream_General, 0, General_ID_String, Decimal_Hexa(Complete_Stream->transport_stream_id), true);
392 }
393 if (!Complete_Stream->network_name.empty())
394 {
395 Fill(Stream_General, 0, General_NetworkName, Complete_Stream->network_name, true);
396 Complete_Stream->network_name.clear();
397 }
398 if (!Complete_Stream->original_network_name.empty())
399 {
400 Fill(Stream_General, 0, General_OriginalNetworkName, Complete_Stream->original_network_name, true);
401 Complete_Stream->original_network_name.clear();
402 }
403 Ztring Countries;
404 Ztring TimeZones;
405 for (std::map<Ztring, Ztring>::iterator TimeZone=Complete_Stream->TimeZones.begin(); TimeZone!=Complete_Stream->TimeZones.end(); ++TimeZone)
406 {
407 Countries+=TimeZone->first+__T(" / ");
408 TimeZones+=TimeZone->second+__T(" / ");
409 }
410 if (!Countries.empty())
411 {
412 Countries.resize(Countries.size()-3);
413 Fill(Stream_General, 0, General_Country, Countries, true);
414 Complete_Stream->TimeZones.clear();
415 }
416 if (!TimeZones.empty())
417 {
418 TimeZones.resize(TimeZones.size()-3);
419 Fill(Stream_General, 0, General_TimeZone, TimeZones, true);
420 Complete_Stream->TimeZones.clear();
421 }
422 if (!Complete_Stream->Duration_Start.empty())
423 {
424 Fill(Stream_General, 0, General_Duration_Start, Complete_Stream->Duration_Start, true);
425 Complete_Stream->Duration_Start.clear();
426 }
427 complete_stream::transport_streams::iterator Transport_Stream=Complete_Stream->transport_stream_id_IsValid?Complete_Stream->Transport_Streams.find(Complete_Stream->transport_stream_id):Complete_Stream->Transport_Streams.end();
428 if (Transport_Stream!=Complete_Stream->Transport_Streams.end())
429 {
430 //TS info
431 for (std::map<std::string, ZenLib::Ztring>::iterator Info=Transport_Stream->second.Infos.begin(); Info!=Transport_Stream->second.Infos.end(); ++Info)
432 Fill(Stream_General, 0, Info->first.c_str(), Info->second, true);
433 Transport_Stream->second.Infos.clear();
434
435 //Per source (ATSC)
436 if (Transport_Stream->second.source_id_IsValid)
437 {
438 complete_stream::sources::iterator Source=Complete_Stream->Sources.find(Transport_Stream->second.source_id);
439 if (Source!=Complete_Stream->Sources.end())
440 {
441 if (!Source->second.texts.empty())
442 {
443 Ztring Texts;
444 for (std::map<int16u, Ztring>::iterator text=Source->second.texts.begin(); text!=Source->second.texts.end(); ++text)
445 Texts+=text->second+__T(" - ");
446 if (!Texts.empty())
447 Texts.resize(Texts.size()-3);
448 Fill(Stream_General, 0, General_ServiceProvider, Texts);
449 }
450 }
451 }
452
453 //Per program
454 for (complete_stream::transport_stream::programs::iterator Program=Transport_Stream->second.Programs.begin(); Program!=Transport_Stream->second.Programs.end(); ++Program)
455 {
456 if (Program->second.IsParsed)
457 {
458 //Per pid
459 Ztring Languages, Codecs, Formats, StreamKinds, StreamPoss, elementary_PIDs, elementary_PIDs_String, Delay, LawRating, Title;
460 for (size_t Pos=0; Pos<Program->second.elementary_PIDs.size(); Pos++)
461 {
462 int16u elementary_PID=Program->second.elementary_PIDs[Pos];
463 if (PerStream_AlwaysParse || Complete_Stream->Streams[elementary_PID]->IsRegistered)
464 {
465 if (!Complete_Stream->Streams[elementary_PID]->Teletexts.empty())
466 {
467 for (std::map<int16u, teletext>::iterator Teletext=Complete_Stream->Streams[elementary_PID]->Teletexts.begin(); Teletext!=Complete_Stream->Streams[elementary_PID]->Teletexts.end(); ++Teletext)
468 {
469 Ztring Format;
470 Ztring Language;
471 if (Teletext->second.StreamKind!=Stream_Max)
472 {
473 StreamKinds+=Ztring::ToZtring(Teletext->second.StreamKind);
474 StreamPoss+=Ztring::ToZtring(Teletext->second.StreamPos);
475 Format=Retrieve(Teletext->second.StreamKind, Teletext->second.StreamPos, "Format");
476 Language=Retrieve(Teletext->second.StreamKind, Teletext->second.StreamPos, "Language");
477 }
478 Formats+=Format+__T(" / ");
479 Codecs+=Format+__T(" / ");
480 StreamKinds+=__T(" / ");
481 StreamPoss+=__T(" / ");
482 elementary_PIDs+=Ztring::ToZtring(elementary_PID)+__T('-')+Ztring::ToZtring(Teletext->first)+__T(" / ");
483 Languages+=Language+__T(" / ");
484 Ztring List_String=Decimal_Hexa(elementary_PID)+__T('-')+Ztring::ToZtring(Teletext->first);
485 List_String+=__T(" (");
486 List_String+=Format;
487 if (!Language.empty())
488 {
489 List_String+=__T(", ");
490 List_String+=Language;
491 }
492 List_String+=__T(")");
493 elementary_PIDs_String+=List_String+__T(" / ");
494 }
495 }
496 else
497 {
498 Ztring Format=Retrieve(Complete_Stream->Streams[elementary_PID]->StreamKind, Complete_Stream->Streams[elementary_PID]->StreamPos, Fill_Parameter(Complete_Stream->Streams[elementary_PID]->StreamKind, Generic_Format));
499 if (Format.empty())
500 Format=Mpeg_Psi_stream_type_Format(Complete_Stream->Streams[elementary_PID]->stream_type, Program->second.registration_format_identifier);
501 if (Format.empty())
502 {
503 std::map<std::string, Ztring>::iterator Format_FromInfo=Complete_Stream->Streams[elementary_PID]->Infos.find("Format");
504 if (Format_FromInfo!=Complete_Stream->Streams[elementary_PID]->Infos.end())
505 Format=Format_FromInfo->second;
506 }
507 if (Format.empty())
508 Program->second.HasNotDisplayableStreams=true;
509 Formats+=Format+__T(" / ");
510 Codecs+=Retrieve(Complete_Stream->Streams[elementary_PID]->StreamKind, Complete_Stream->Streams[elementary_PID]->StreamPos, Fill_Parameter(Complete_Stream->Streams[elementary_PID]->StreamKind, Generic_Codec))+__T(" / ");
511 if (Complete_Stream->Streams[elementary_PID]->StreamKind!=Stream_Max)
512 {
513 StreamKinds+=Ztring::ToZtring(Complete_Stream->Streams[elementary_PID]->StreamKind);
514 StreamPoss+=Ztring::ToZtring(Complete_Stream->Streams[elementary_PID]->StreamPos);
515 }
516 StreamKinds+=__T(" / ");
517 StreamPoss+=__T(" / ");
518 elementary_PIDs+=Ztring::ToZtring(elementary_PID)+__T(" / ");
519 Ztring Language=Retrieve(Complete_Stream->Streams[elementary_PID]->StreamKind, Complete_Stream->Streams[elementary_PID]->StreamPos, "Language/String");
520 Languages+=Language+__T(" / ");
521 Ztring List_String=Decimal_Hexa(elementary_PID);
522 List_String+=__T(" (");
523 List_String+=Format;
524 if (!Language.empty())
525 {
526 List_String+=__T(", ");
527 List_String+=Language;
528 }
529 List_String+=__T(")");
530 elementary_PIDs_String+=List_String+__T(" / ");
531 }
532
533 if (Complete_Stream->Streams[elementary_PID]->IsPCR)
534 {
535 Delay=Ztring::ToZtring(((float64)Complete_Stream->Streams[elementary_PID]->TimeStamp_Start)/27000, 6);
536 }
537
538 //Law rating
539 if (Complete_Stream->Streams[elementary_PID] && Complete_Stream->Streams[elementary_PID]->Parser)
540 {
541 Ztring LawRating_Temp=Complete_Stream->Streams[elementary_PID]->Parser->Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, General_LawRating);
542 if (!LawRating_Temp.empty())
543 LawRating+=LawRating_Temp+__T(" / ");;
544 Ztring Title_Temp=Complete_Stream->Streams[elementary_PID]->Parser->Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, General_Title);
545 if (!Title_Temp.empty())
546 Title+=Title_Temp+__T(" / ");
547 }
548 }
549 }
550
551 if (Program->second.Update_Needed_Info || Program->second.Update_Needed_IsRegistered || Program->second.Update_Needed_StreamCount || Program->second.Update_Needed_StreamPos)
552 {
553 if (!Transport_Stream->second.Programs.empty()
554 && (Transport_Stream->second.Programs.size()>1
555 || Transport_Stream->second.Programs.begin()->second.HasNotDisplayableStreams
556 || !Transport_Stream->second.Programs.begin()->second.Infos.empty()
557 || !Transport_Stream->second.Programs.begin()->second.DVB_EPG_Blocks.empty()
558 || (Transport_Stream->second.Programs.begin()->second.source_id_IsValid && Complete_Stream->Sources.find(Transport_Stream->second.Programs.begin()->second.source_id)!=Complete_Stream->Sources.end())
559 || Config->File_MpegTs_ForceMenu_Get()))
560 {
561 if (Program->second.StreamPos==(size_t)-1)
562 {
563 size_t StreamPos=(size_t)-1;
564 for (size_t program_number=0; program_number<Complete_Stream->program_number_Order.size(); program_number++)
565 if (Program->first<Complete_Stream->program_number_Order[program_number])
566 {
567 StreamPos=program_number;
568 for (size_t program_number2=program_number; program_number2<Complete_Stream->program_number_Order.size(); program_number2++)
569 Transport_Stream->second.Programs[Complete_Stream->program_number_Order[program_number2]].StreamPos++;
570 Complete_Stream->program_number_Order.insert(Complete_Stream->program_number_Order.begin()+program_number, Program->first);
571 break;
572 }
573 if (StreamPos==(size_t)-1)
574 {
575 Complete_Stream->program_number_Order.push_back(Program->first);
576 }
577
578 Stream_Prepare(Stream_Menu, StreamPos);
579 Program->second.StreamPos=StreamPos_Last;
580 }
581 else
582 StreamPos_Last=Program->second.StreamPos;
583 Fill(Stream_Menu, StreamPos_Last, Menu_ID, Program->second.pid, 10, true);
584 Fill(Stream_Menu, StreamPos_Last, Menu_ID_String, Decimal_Hexa(Program->second.pid), true);
585 Fill(Stream_Menu, StreamPos_Last, Menu_MenuID, Program->first, 10, true);
586 Fill(Stream_Menu, StreamPos_Last, Menu_MenuID_String, Decimal_Hexa(Program->first), true);
587 Clear(Stream_Menu, StreamPos_Last, General_StreamOrder);
588 for (size_t programs_List_Pos=0; programs_List_Pos<Transport_Stream->second.programs_List.size(); ++programs_List_Pos)
589 if (Transport_Stream->second.programs_List[programs_List_Pos]==Program->first)
590 Fill(Stream_Menu, StreamPos_Last, General_StreamOrder, programs_List_Pos);
591 for (std::map<std::string, ZenLib::Ztring>::iterator Info=Program->second.Infos.begin(); Info!=Program->second.Infos.end(); ++Info)
592 Fill(Stream_Menu, StreamPos_Last, Info->first.c_str(), Info->second, true);
593 Program->second.Infos.clear();
594 for (std::map<std::string, ZenLib::Ztring>::iterator Info=Program->second.ExtraInfos_Content.begin(); Info!=Program->second.ExtraInfos_Content.end(); ++Info)
595 Fill(Stream_Menu, StreamPos_Last, Info->first.c_str(), Info->second, true);
596 Program->second.ExtraInfos_Content.clear();
597 for (std::map<std::string, ZenLib::Ztring>::iterator Info=Program->second.ExtraInfos_Option.begin(); Info!=Program->second.ExtraInfos_Option.end(); ++Info)
598 (*Stream_More)[Stream_Menu][StreamPos_Last](Ztring().From_Local(Info->first.c_str()), Info_Options)=Info->second;
599 Program->second.ExtraInfos_Option.clear();
600
601 if (!Formats.empty())
602 Formats.resize(Formats.size()-3);
603 Fill(Stream_Menu, StreamPos_Last, Menu_Format, Formats, true);
604 if (!Codecs.empty())
605 Codecs.resize(Codecs.size()-3);
606 Fill(Stream_Menu, StreamPos_Last, Menu_Codec, Codecs, true);
607 if (!StreamKinds.empty())
608 StreamKinds.resize(StreamKinds.size()-3);
609 Fill(Stream_Menu, StreamPos_Last, Menu_List_StreamKind, StreamKinds, true);
610 if (!elementary_PIDs_String.empty())
611 elementary_PIDs_String.resize(elementary_PIDs_String.size()-3);
612 Fill(Stream_Menu, StreamPos_Last, Menu_List_String, elementary_PIDs_String, true);
613 if (!elementary_PIDs.empty())
614 elementary_PIDs.resize(elementary_PIDs.size()-3);
615 Fill(Stream_Menu, StreamPos_Last, Menu_List, elementary_PIDs, true);
616 if (!StreamPoss.empty())
617 StreamPoss.resize(StreamPoss.size()-3);
618 Fill(Stream_Menu, StreamPos_Last, Menu_List_StreamPos, StreamPoss, true);
619 if (!Languages.empty())
620 Languages.resize(Languages.size()-3);
621 Fill(Stream_Menu, StreamPos_Last, Menu_Language, Languages, true);
622 if (!LawRating.empty())
623 LawRating.resize(LawRating.size()-3);
624 Fill(Stream_Menu, StreamPos_Last, "LawRating", LawRating, true);
625 if (StreamPos_Last)
626 Clear(Stream_General, 0, General_LawRating); //More than 1 menu, can not be in General part
627 if (!Title.empty())
628 Title.resize(Title.size()-3);
629 Fill(Stream_Menu, StreamPos_Last, "Title", Title, true);
630 if (StreamPos_Last)
631 Clear(Stream_General, 0, General_Title); //More than 1 menu, can not be in General part
632 }
633 }
634
635 //Delay
636 if (Program->second.Update_Needed_IsRegistered)
637 {
638 switch (Count_Get(Stream_Menu))
639 {
640 case 0 : Fill(Stream_General, 0, General_Delay, Delay, true); break;
641 default: Fill(Stream_Menu, StreamPos_Last, Menu_Delay, Delay, true); break;
642 }
643 Program->second.Update_Needed_IsRegistered=false;
644 }
645 if (Count_Get(Stream_Menu)==2)
646 Clear(Stream_General, 0, General_Delay); //Not valid, multiple menus
647 }
648 }
649 }
650
651 //Commercial name
652 if (Count_Get(Stream_Video)==1
653 && Count_Get(Stream_Audio)==1
654 && Retrieve(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Format)==__T("MPEG Video")
655 && Retrieve(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Format_Commercial_IfAny).find(__T("HDV"))==0
656 && Retrieve(Stream_Audio, 0, Audio_Format)==__T("MPEG Audio")
657 && Retrieve(Stream_Audio, 0, Audio_Format_Version)==__T("Version 1")
658 && Retrieve(Stream_Audio, 0, Audio_Format_Profile)==__T("Layer 2")
659 && Retrieve(Stream_Audio, 0, Audio_BitRate)==__T("384000"))
660 Fill(Stream_General, 0, General_Format_Commercial_IfAny, Retrieve(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Format_Commercial_IfAny));
661}

663//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
664void File_MpegTs::Streams_Update_Programs_PerStream(size_t StreamID)
665{
666 complete_stream::stream* Temp=Complete_Stream->Streams[StreamID];
667
668 //No direct handling of Sub streams;
669 if (Temp->stream_type==0x20 && Temp->SubStream_pid) //Stereoscopic is not alone
670 return;
671
672 if (Temp->Parser)
673 Temp->Parser->Open_Buffer_Update();
674
675 //Merging from a previous merge
676 size_t Counts[Stream_Max];
677 for (size_t StreamKind=Stream_General+1; StreamKind<Stream_Max; StreamKind++)
678 Counts[StreamKind]=Count_Get((stream_t)StreamKind);
679 if (Temp->StreamKind != Stream_Max && Temp->StreamPos != (size_t)-1 && Temp->Parser)
680 {
681 Merge(*Temp->Parser, Temp->StreamKind, 0, Temp->StreamPos);
682 StreamKind_Last=Temp->StreamKind;
683 StreamPos_Last=Temp->StreamPos;
684 }
685 else
686 {
687 //By the parser
688 StreamKind_Last=Stream_Max;
689 if (Temp->Parser && Temp->Parser->Status[IsAccepted])
690 {
691 if (Temp->SubStream_pid!=0x0000) //With a substream
692 Fill(Complete_Stream->Streams[Temp->SubStream_pid]->Parser);
693 if (Temp->Parser->Count_Get(Stream_Video) && Temp->Parser->Count_Get(Stream_Text))
694 {
695 //Special case: Video and Text are together
696 Stream_Prepare(Stream_Video);
697 Merge(*Temp->Parser, Stream_Video, 0, StreamPos_Last);
698 }
699 else
700 Merge(*Temp->Parser);
701
702 //More from the FMC parser
703 if (Temp->FMC_ES_ID_IsValid)
704 {
705 complete_stream::transport_stream::iod_ess::iterator IOD_ES=Complete_Stream->Transport_Streams[Complete_Stream->transport_stream_id].IOD_ESs.find(Temp->FMC_ES_ID);
706 if (IOD_ES!=Complete_Stream->Transport_Streams[Complete_Stream->transport_stream_id].IOD_ESs.end() && IOD_ES->second.Parser)
707 {
708 Finish(IOD_ES->second.Parser);
709 Merge(*IOD_ES->second.Parser, StreamKind_Last, StreamPos_Last, 0);
710 }
711 }
712
713 //LATM
714 complete_stream::transport_stream::iod_ess::iterator IOD_ES=Complete_Stream->Transport_Streams[Complete_Stream->transport_stream_id].IOD_ESs.find(Complete_Stream->Streams[StreamID]->FMC_ES_ID);
715 #ifdef MEDIAINFO_MPEG4_YES
716 if (IOD_ES!=Complete_Stream->Transport_Streams[Complete_Stream->transport_stream_id].IOD_ESs.end() && IOD_ES->second.SLConfig && Retrieve(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, Audio_MuxingMode).empty())
717 Fill(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, Audio_MuxingMode, "SL");
718 #endif
719 if (Complete_Stream->Streams[StreamID]->stream_type==0x11 && Retrieve(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, Audio_MuxingMode).empty())
720 Fill(Stream_Audio, StreamPos_Last, Audio_MuxingMode, "LATM");
721 }
722
723 //By the descriptors
724 if (StreamKind_Last==Stream_Max && Complete_Stream->transport_stream_id_IsValid && !Temp->program_numbers.empty() && !Complete_Stream->Transport_Streams[Complete_Stream->transport_stream_id].Programs.empty())
725 {
726 int32u format_identifier=Complete_Stream->Transport_Streams[Complete_Stream->transport_stream_id].Programs[Temp->program_numbers[0]].registration_format_identifier;
727 if (Temp->IsRegistered
728 && Mpeg_Descriptors_registration_format_identifier_StreamKind(format_identifier)!=Stream_Max)
729 {
730 StreamKind_Last=Mpeg_Descriptors_registration_format_identifier_StreamKind(format_identifier);
731 Stream_Prepare(StreamKind_Last);
732 Fill(StreamKind_Last, StreamPos_Last, Fill_Parameter(StreamKind_Last, Generic_Format), Mpeg_Descriptors_registration_format_identifier_Format(format_identifier));
733 Fill(StreamKind_Last, StreamPos_Last, Fill_Parameter(StreamKind_Last, Generic_Codec), Mpeg_Descriptors_registration_format_identifier_Format(format_identifier));
734 }
735 }
736
737 //By registration_format_identifier
738 if (StreamKind_Last==Stream_Max && Temp->registration_format_identifier && Temp->IsRegistered && Mpeg_Descriptors_registration_format_identifier_StreamKind(Temp->registration_format_identifier)!=Stream_Max)
739 {
740 StreamKind_Last=Mpeg_Descriptors_registration_format_identifier_StreamKind(Temp->registration_format_identifier);
741 Stream_Prepare(StreamKind_Last);
742 Fill(StreamKind_Last, StreamPos_Last, Fill_Parameter(StreamKind_Last, Generic_Format), Mpeg_Descriptors_registration_format_identifier_Format(Temp->registration_format_identifier));
743 Fill(StreamKind_Last, StreamPos_Last, Fill_Parameter(StreamKind_Last, Generic_Codec), Mpeg_Descriptors_registration_format_identifier_Format(Temp->registration_format_identifier));
744 }
745
746 //By the stream_type
747 if (StreamKind_Last==Stream_Max && Complete_Stream->transport_stream_id_IsValid && !Temp->program_numbers.empty() && !Complete_Stream->Transport_Streams[Complete_Stream->transport_stream_id].Programs.empty())
748 {
749 int32u format_identifier=Complete_Stream->Transport_Streams[Complete_Stream->transport_stream_id].Programs[Temp->program_numbers[0]].registration_format_identifier;
750 if (Mpeg_Psi_stream_type_StreamKind(Temp->stream_type, format_identifier)!=Stream_Max && (Temp->IsRegistered || ForceStreamDisplay || format_identifier==Elements::HDMV))
751 {
752 StreamKind_Last=Mpeg_Psi_stream_type_StreamKind(Temp->stream_type, format_identifier);
753 if (StreamKind_Last==Stream_General && Temp->Parser) //Only information, no streams
754 {
755 Merge (*Temp->Parser, Stream_General, 0, 0);
756 StreamKind_Last=Stream_Max;
757 }
758 Stream_Prepare(StreamKind_Last);
759 Fill(StreamKind_Last, StreamPos_Last, Fill_Parameter(StreamKind_Last, Generic_Format), Mpeg_Psi_stream_type_Format(Temp->stream_type, format_identifier));
760 Fill(StreamKind_Last, StreamPos_Last, Fill_Parameter(StreamKind_Last, Generic_Codec), Mpeg_Psi_stream_type_Codec(Temp->stream_type, format_identifier));
761 }
762 }
763
764 //By the StreamKind
765 if (StreamKind_Last==Stream_Max && Temp->StreamKind_FromDescriptor!=Stream_Max && (Temp->IsRegistered || ForceStreamDisplay || (!Temp->program_numbers.empty() && Complete_Stream->Transport_Streams[Complete_Stream->transport_stream_id].Programs[Temp->program_numbers[0]].registration_format_identifier==Elements::HDMV)))
766 {
767 Stream_Prepare(Temp->StreamKind_FromDescriptor);
768 }
769 }
770
771 //More info
772 if (StreamKind_Last!=Stream_Max)
773 {
774 for (size_t StreamKind=Stream_General+1; StreamKind<Stream_Max; StreamKind++)
775 {
776 size_t Counts_Now=Count_Get((stream_t)StreamKind);
777 for (size_t StreamPos=Counts[StreamKind]; StreamPos<Counts_Now; StreamPos++)
778 {
779 Temp->StreamKind=StreamKind_Last;
780 Temp->StreamPos=StreamPos;
781
782 //Encryption
783 if (Temp->CA_system_ID)
784 Fill((stream_t)StreamKind, StreamPos, "Encryption", Mpeg_Descriptors_CA_system_ID(Temp->CA_system_ID));
785 else if (Temp->Scrambled_Count>16)
786 Fill((stream_t)StreamKind, StreamPos, "Encryption", "Encrypted");
787
788 //TS info
789 for (std::map<std::string, ZenLib::Ztring>::iterator Info=Temp->Infos.begin(); Info!=Temp->Infos.end(); ++Info)
790 {
791 if (Retrieve((stream_t)StreamKind, StreamPos, Info->first.c_str()).empty())
792 {
793 //Special case : DTS Neural
794 if ((stream_t)StreamKind==Stream_Audio && Info->first=="Matrix_ChannelPositions" && Info->second.find(__T("DTS Neural Audio "))==0)
795 {
796 int8u Channels=Retrieve(Stream_Audio, StreamPos, Audio_Channel_s_).To_int8u();
797 if (Channels)
798 {
799 int8u config_id=Ztring(Info->second.substr(17, string::npos)).To_int8u();
800 int8u Matrix_Channels=MpegTs_DtsNeural_Channels(Channels, config_id);
801 if (Matrix_Channels)
802 {
803 Fill(Stream_Audio, StreamPos, Audio_Matrix_Channel_s_, Matrix_Channels);
804 Fill(Stream_Audio, StreamPos, Audio_Matrix_ChannelPositions, MpegTs_DtsNeural_ChannelPositions(Channels, config_id));
805 Fill(Stream_Audio, StreamPos, Audio_ChannelPositions_String2, MpegTs_DtsNeural_ChannelPositions2(Channels, config_id));
806 }
807 }
808
809 }
810 else
811 Fill((stream_t)StreamKind, StreamPos, Info->first.c_str(), Info->second, true);
812 }
813 }
814 for (std::map<std::string, ZenLib::Ztring>::iterator Info=Temp->Infos_Option.begin(); Info!=Temp->Infos_Option.end(); ++Info)
815 (*Stream_More)[(stream_t)StreamKind][StreamPos](Ztring().From_Local(Info->first.c_str()), Info_Options)=Info->second;
816
817 //Common
818 if (Temp->SubStream_pid!=0x0000) //Wit a substream
819 {
820 Ztring Format_Profile=Retrieve(Stream_Video, StreamPos, Video_Format_Profile);
821 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos, Video_ID, Ztring::ToZtring(Temp->SubStream_pid)+__T(" / ")+Ztring::ToZtring(StreamID), true);
822 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos, Video_ID_String, Decimal_Hexa(Temp->SubStream_pid)+__T(" / ")+Decimal_Hexa(StreamID), true);
823 if (!Format_Profile.empty() && Complete_Stream->Streams[Temp->SubStream_pid] && Complete_Stream->Streams[Temp->SubStream_pid]->Parser)
824 Fill(Stream_Video, StreamPos, Video_Format_Profile, Complete_Stream->Streams[Temp->SubStream_pid]->Parser->Retrieve(Stream_Video, 0, Video_Format_Profile)+__T(" / ")+Format_Profile, true);
825 }
826 else if (Retrieve((stream_t)StreamKind, StreamPos, General_ID).find(__T('-'))!=string::npos)
827 {
828 Ztring ID=Retrieve((stream_t)StreamKind, StreamPos, General_ID);
829 size_t ID_Pos=ID.find(__T('-'));
830 if (ID_Pos!=string::npos)
831 ID.erase(ID.begin(), ID.begin()+ID_Pos+1); //Removing the PS part
832 Ztring ID_String=Retrieve((stream_t)StreamKind, StreamPos, General_ID_String);
833 size_t ID_String_Pos=ID_String.find(__T('-'));
834 if (ID_String_Pos!=string::npos)
835 ID_String.erase(ID_String.begin(), ID_String.begin()+ID_String_Pos+1); //Removing the PS part
836 #ifdef MEDIAINFO_ARIBSTDB24B37_YES
837 if (FromAribStdB24B37)
838 {
839 Fill((stream_t)StreamKind, StreamPos, General_ID, ID, true);
840 Fill((stream_t)StreamKind, StreamPos, General_ID_String, ID_String, true);
841 }
842 else
843 #endif //MEDIAINFO_ARIBSTDB24B37_YES
844 {
845 Fill((stream_t)StreamKind, StreamPos, General_ID, Ztring::ToZtring(StreamID)+__T('-')+ID, true);
846 Fill((stream_t)StreamKind, StreamPos, General_ID_String, Decimal_Hexa(StreamID)+__T('-')+ID_String, true);
847 }
848 }
849 else
850 {
851 Fill((stream_t)StreamKind, StreamPos, General_ID, StreamID, 10, true);
852 Fill((stream_t)StreamKind, StreamPos, General_ID_String, Decimal_Hexa(StreamID), true);
853 }
854 for (size_t Pos=0; Pos<Temp->program_numbers.size(); Pos++)
855 {
856 Fill((stream_t)StreamKind, StreamPos, General_MenuID, Temp->program_numbers[Pos], 10, Pos==0);
857 Fill((stream_t)StreamKind, StreamPos, General_MenuID_String, Decimal_Hexa(Temp->program_numbers[Pos]), Pos==0);
858 }
859
860 //StreamOrder
861 Clear((stream_t)StreamKind, StreamPos, General_StreamOrder);
862 for (size_t program_FromStream=0; program_FromStream<Temp->program_numbers.size(); ++program_FromStream)
863 {
864 int16u program_number=Temp->program_numbers[program_FromStream];
865 std::vector<int16u> &programs_List=Complete_Stream->Transport_Streams[Complete_Stream->transport_stream_id].programs_List;
866 size_t programs_List_Pos=0;
867 for (; programs_List_Pos<programs_List.size(); ++programs_List_Pos)
868 if (programs_List[programs_List_Pos]==program_number)
869 break;
870 if (programs_List_Pos<programs_List.size())
871 {
872 complete_stream::transport_stream::program &Program=Complete_Stream->Transport_Streams[Complete_Stream->transport_stream_id].Programs[program_number];
873 for (size_t elementary_PID_Pos=0; elementary_PID_Pos<Program.elementary_PIDs.size(); ++elementary_PID_Pos)
874 if (Program.elementary_PIDs[elementary_PID_Pos]==StreamID)
875 Fill((stream_t)StreamKind, StreamPos, General_StreamOrder, Ztring::ToZtring(programs_List_Pos)+__T('-')+Ztring::ToZtring(elementary_PID_Pos));
876 }
877 }
878
879 //Special cases
880 if ((stream_t)StreamKind==Stream_Video && Temp->Parser && Temp->Parser->Count_Get(Stream_Text))
881 {
882 }
883 }
884 }
885 Temp->Infos.clear();
886 Temp->Infos_Option.clear();
887
888 //Special cases
889 if (Temp->Parser && Temp->Parser->Count_Get(Stream_Video))
890 {
891 //Video and Text may be together
892 size_t Text_Count=Temp->Parser->Count_Get(Stream_Text);
893 for (size_t Text_Pos=0; Text_Pos<Text_Count; Text_Pos++)
894 {
895 Ztring Parser_ID=Temp->Parser->Retrieve(Stream_Text, Text_Pos, Text_ID);
896 if (Parser_ID.find(__T('-'))!=string::npos)
897 Parser_ID.erase(Parser_ID.begin(), Parser_ID.begin()+Parser_ID.find(__T('-'))+1);
898 Ztring ID=Retrieve(Stream_Video, Temp->StreamPos, Video_ID)+__T('-')+Parser_ID;
899 Ztring ID_String=Retrieve(Stream_Video, Temp->StreamPos, Video_ID_String)+__T('-')+Parser_ID;
900 StreamPos_Last=(size_t)-1;
901 for (size_t Pos=0; Pos<Count_Get(Stream_Text); Pos++)
902 if (Retrieve(Stream_Text, Pos, Text_ID)==ID && Retrieve(Stream_Text, Pos, "MuxingMode")==Temp->Parser->Retrieve(Stream_Text, Text_Pos, "MuxingMode"))
903 {
904 StreamPos_Last=Pos;
905 break;
906 }
907 if (StreamPos_Last==(size_t)-1)
908 Stream_Prepare(Stream_Text, StreamPos_Last);
909 if (!IsSub)
910 Fill(Stream_Text, StreamPos_Last, "MuxingMode_MoreInfo", __T("Muxed in Video #")+Ztring().From_Number(Temp->StreamPos+1), true);
911 Merge(*Temp->Parser, Stream_Text, Text_Pos, StreamPos_Last);
912
913 Fill(Stream_Text, StreamPos_Last, Text_ID, ID, true);
914 Fill(Stream_Text, StreamPos_Last, Text_ID_String, ID_String, true);
915 Fill(Stream_Text, StreamPos_Last, Text_StreamOrder, Retrieve(Stream_Video, Temp->StreamPos, Video_StreamOrder), true);
916 Fill(Stream_Text, StreamPos_Last, Text_MenuID, Retrieve(Stream_Video, Temp->StreamPos, Video_MenuID), true);
917 Fill(Stream_Text, StreamPos_Last, Text_MenuID_String, Retrieve(Stream_Video, Temp->StreamPos, Video_MenuID_String), true);
918 Fill(Stream_Text, StreamPos_Last, Text_Duration, Retrieve(Stream_Video, Temp->StreamPos, Video_Duration), true);
919 Fill(Stream_Text, StreamPos_Last, Text_Delay, Retrieve(Stream_Video, Temp->StreamPos, Video_Delay), true);
920 Fill(Stream_Text, StreamPos_Last, Text_Delay_Source, Retrieve(Stream_Video, Temp->StreamPos, Video_Delay_Source), true);
921 }
922
923 StreamKind_Last=Temp->StreamKind;
924 StreamPos_Last=Temp->StreamPos;
925 }
926 }
927
928 //Teletext
929 if (StreamKind_Last==Stream_Max)
930 {
931 for (std::map<int16u, teletext>::iterator Teletext=Temp->Teletexts.begin(); Teletext!=Temp->Teletexts.end(); ++Teletext)
932 {
933 std::map<std::string, Ztring>::iterator Info_Format=Teletext->second.Infos.find("Format");
934 Stream_Prepare((Info_Format!=Teletext->second.Infos.end() && Info_Format->second==__T("Teletext"))?Stream_Other:Stream_Text);
935 Fill(StreamKind_Last, StreamPos_Last, General_ID, Ztring::ToZtring(StreamID)+__T('-')+Ztring::ToZtring(Teletext->first), true);
936 Fill(StreamKind_Last, StreamPos_Last, General_ID_String, Decimal_Hexa(StreamID)+__T('-')+Ztring::ToZtring(Teletext->first), true);
937
938 for (size_t Pos=0; Pos<Temp->program_numbers.size(); Pos++)
939 {
940 Fill(StreamKind_Last, StreamPos_Last, General_MenuID, Temp->program_numbers[Pos], 10, Pos==0);
941 Fill(StreamKind_Last, StreamPos_Last, General_MenuID_String, Decimal_Hexa(Temp->program_numbers[Pos]), Pos==0);
942 }
943
944 //TS info
945 for (std::map<std::string, ZenLib::Ztring>::iterator Info=Teletext->second.Infos.begin(); Info!=Teletext->second.Infos.end(); ++Info)
946 {
947 if (Retrieve(StreamKind_Last, StreamPos_Last, Info->first.c_str()).empty())
948 Fill(StreamKind_Last, StreamPos_Last, Info->first.c_str(), Info->second);
949 }
950 Teletext->second.Infos.clear();
951 Teletext->second.StreamKind=StreamKind_Last;
952 Teletext->second.StreamPos=StreamPos_Last;
953 }
954 }
955
956 //Law rating
957 if (Temp->Parser)
958 {
959 Ztring LawRating=Temp->Parser->Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, General_LawRating);
960 if (!LawRating.empty())
961 {
962 if (Count_Get(Stream_Menu))
963 {
964 Ztring MenuID=Retrieve(Temp->StreamKind, Temp->StreamPos, General_MenuID);
965 for (size_t Pos=0; Pos<Count_Get(Stream_Menu); Pos++)
966 if (Retrieve(Stream_Menu, Pos, General_MenuID)==MenuID)
967 Fill(Stream_Menu, Pos, "LawRating", LawRating, true);
968 }
969 else
970 Fill(Stream_General, 0, General_LawRating, LawRating, true);
971 }
972 }
973
974 //Title
975 if (Temp->Parser)
976 {
977 Ztring Title=Temp->Parser->Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, General_Title);
978 if (!Title.empty() && Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, General_Title).empty())
979 {
980 if (Count_Get(Stream_Menu))
981 {
982 Ztring MenuID=Retrieve(Temp->StreamKind, Temp->StreamPos, General_MenuID);
983 for (size_t Pos=0; Pos<Count_Get(Stream_Menu); Pos++)
984 if (Retrieve(Stream_Menu, Pos, General_MenuID)==MenuID)
985 Fill(Stream_Menu, Pos, "Title", Title, true);
986 }
987 else
988 Fill(Stream_General, 0, General_Title, Title);
989 }
990 }
991}
992
993//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
994void File_MpegTs::Streams_Update_EPG()
995{
996 //EPG
997 complete_stream::transport_streams::iterator Transport_Stream=Complete_Stream->transport_stream_id_IsValid?Complete_Stream->Transport_Streams.find(Complete_Stream->transport_stream_id):Complete_Stream->Transport_Streams.end();
998 if (Transport_Stream==Complete_Stream->Transport_Streams.end())
999 return;
1000
1001 //Per source (ATSC)
1002 if (Transport_Stream->second.source_id_IsValid)
1003 {
1004 complete_stream::sources::iterator Source=Complete_Stream->Sources.find(Transport_Stream->second.source_id);
1005 if (Source!=Complete_Stream->Sources.end())
1006 {
1007 //EPG
1008 std::map<Ztring, Ztring> EPGs;
1009 for (complete_stream::source::atsc_epg_blocks::iterator ATSC_EPG_Block=Source->second.ATSC_EPG_Blocks.begin(); ATSC_EPG_Block!=Source->second.ATSC_EPG_Blocks.end(); ++ATSC_EPG_Block)
1010 for (complete_stream::source::atsc_epg_block::events::iterator Event=ATSC_EPG_Block->second.Events.begin(); Event!=ATSC_EPG_Block->second.Events.end(); ++Event)
1011 {
1012 Ztring Texts;
1013 for (std::map<int16u, Ztring>::iterator text=Event->second.texts.begin(); text!=Event->second.texts.end(); ++text)
1014 Texts+=text->second+__T(" - ");
1015 if (!Texts.empty())
1016 Texts.resize(Texts.size()-3);
1017 EPGs[Ztring().Date_From_Seconds_1970(Event->second.start_time+315964800-Complete_Stream->GPS_UTC_offset)]=Event->second.title+__T(" / ")+Texts+__T(" / / / ")+Event->second.duration+__T(" / ");
1018 }
1019 if (!EPGs.empty())
1020 {
1021 //Trashing old EPG
1022 size_t Begin=Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, General_EPG_Positions_Begin).To_int32u();
1023 size_t End=Retrieve(Stream_General, 0, General_EPG_Positions_End).To_int32u();
1024 if (Begin && End && Begin<End)
1025 for (size_t Pos=End-1; Pos>=Begin; Pos--)
1026 Clear(Stream_General, 0, Pos);
1027
1028 //Filling
1029 Fill(Stream_General, 0, General_EPG_Positions_Begin, Count_Get(Stream_General, 0), 10, true);
1030 for (std::map<Ztring, Ztring>::iterator EPG=EPGs.begin(); EPG!=EPGs.end(); ++EPG)
1031 Fill(Stream_General, 0, EPG->first.To_Local().c_str(), EPG->second, true);
1032 Fill(Stream_General, 0, General_EPG_Positions_End, Count_Get(Stream_General, 0), 10, true);
1033 }
1034 }
1035 }
1036
1037 //Per program
1038 if (!Transport_Stream->second.Programs.empty()
1039 && (Transport_Stream->second.Programs.size()>1
1040 || !Transport_Stream->second.Programs.begin()->second.Infos.empty()
1041 || !Transport_Stream->second.Programs.begin()->second.DVB_EPG_Blocks.empty()
1042 || Complete_Stream->Sources.find(Transport_Stream->second.Programs.begin()->second.source_id)!=Complete_Stream->Sources.end()
1043 || Config->File_MpegTs_ForceMenu_Get()))
1044 for (complete_stream::transport_stream::programs::iterator Program=Transport_Stream->second.Programs.begin(); Program!=Transport_Stream->second.Programs.end(); ++Program)
1045 {
1046 if (Program->second.IsParsed)
1047 {
1048 bool EPGs_IsUpdated=false;
1049 std::map<Ztring, Ztring> EPGs;
1050
1051 //EPG - DVB
1052 if (Program->second.DVB_EPG_Blocks_IsUpdated)
1053 {
1054 for (complete_stream::transport_stream::program::dvb_epg_blocks::iterator DVB_EPG_Block=Program->second.DVB_EPG_Blocks.begin(); DVB_EPG_Block!=Program->second.DVB_EPG_Blocks.end(); ++DVB_EPG_Block)
1055 for (complete_stream::transport_stream::program::dvb_epg_block::events::iterator Event=DVB_EPG_Block->second.Events.begin(); Event!=DVB_EPG_Block->second.Events.end(); ++Event)
1056 if (EPGs.find(Event->second.start_time)==EPGs.end() || DVB_EPG_Block->first==0x4E) //Does not exist or "DVB - event_information_section - actual_transport_stream : return present/following"
1057 EPGs[Event->second.start_time]=Event->second.short_event.event_name+__T(" / ")+Event->second.short_event.text+__T(" / ")+Event->second.content+__T(" / / ")+Event->second.duration+__T(" / ")+Event->second.running_status;
1058 Program->second.DVB_EPG_Blocks_IsUpdated=false;
1059 EPGs_IsUpdated=true;
1060 }
1061
1062 //EPG - ATSC
1063 if (Program->second.source_id_IsValid)
1064 {
1065 complete_stream::sources::iterator Source=Complete_Stream->Sources.find(Program->second.source_id);
1066 if (Source!=Complete_Stream->Sources.end())
1067 {
1068 if (!Source->second.texts.empty())
1069 {
1070 Ztring Texts;
1071 for (std::map<int16u, Ztring>::iterator text=Source->second.texts.begin(); text!=Source->second.texts.end(); ++text)
1072 Texts+=text->second+__T(" - ");
1073 if (!Texts.empty())
1074 Texts.resize(Texts.size()-3);
1075 if (Program->second.StreamPos==(size_t)-1)
1076 {
1077 Complete_Stream->program_number_Order.push_back(Program->first);
1078 Stream_Prepare(Stream_Menu);
1079 Program->second.StreamPos=StreamPos_Last;
1080 }
1081 Fill(Stream_Menu, Program->second.StreamPos, Menu_ServiceProvider, Texts, true);
1082 }
1083 if (Source->second.ATSC_EPG_Blocks_IsUpdated)
1084 {
1085 for (complete_stream::source::atsc_epg_blocks::iterator ATSC_EPG_Block=Source->second.ATSC_EPG_Blocks.begin(); ATSC_EPG_Block!=Source->second.ATSC_EPG_Blocks.end(); ++ATSC_EPG_Block)
1086 for (complete_stream::source::atsc_epg_block::events::iterator Event=ATSC_EPG_Block->second.Events.begin(); Event!=ATSC_EPG_Block->second.Events.end(); ++Event)
1087 if (Event->second.start_time!=(int32u)-1) //TODO: find the reason when start_time is not set
1088 {
1089 Ztring Texts;
1090 for (std::map<int16u, Ztring>::iterator text=Event->second.texts.begin(); text!=Event->second.texts.end(); ++text)
1091 Texts+=text->second+__T(" - ");
1092 if (!Texts.empty())
1093 Texts.resize(Texts.size()-3);
1094 EPGs[Ztring().Date_From_Seconds_1970(Event->second.start_time+315964800-Complete_Stream->GPS_UTC_offset)]=Event->second.title+__T(" / ")+Texts+__T(" / / / ")+Event->second.duration+__T(" / ");
1095 }
1096 Source->second.ATSC_EPG_Blocks_IsUpdated=false;
1097 EPGs_IsUpdated=true;
1098 }
1099 }
1100 }
1101
1102 //EPG - Filling
1103 if (EPGs_IsUpdated)
1104 {
1105 if (Program->second.StreamPos==(size_t)-1)
1106 {
1107 Complete_Stream->program_number_Order.push_back(Program->first);
1108 Stream_Prepare(Stream_Menu);
1109 Program->second.StreamPos=StreamPos_Last;
1110 }
1111
1112 Program->second.EPGs=EPGs;
1113 Streams_Update_EPG_PerProgram(Program);
1114 }
1115 }
1116 }
1117
1118 Complete_Stream->Sources_IsUpdated=false;
1119 Complete_Stream->Programs_IsUpdated=false;
1120}

1123void File_MpegTs::Streams_Update_EPG_PerProgram(complete_stream::transport_stream::programs::iterator Program)
1124{
1125 size_t Chapters_Pos_Begin=Retrieve(Stream_Menu, Program->second.StreamPos, Menu_Chapters_Pos_Begin).To_int32u();
1126 size_t Chapters_Pos_End=Retrieve(Stream_Menu, Program->second.StreamPos, Menu_Chapters_Pos_End).To_int32u();

1143//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
1144#ifdef MEDIAINFO_MPEGTS_PCR_YES
1145void File_MpegTs::Streams_Update_Duration_Update()
1146{
1147 bool IsVbr=false;
1148 bool IsCbr=false;
1149 #if MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED
1150 float64 TimeStamp_InstantaneousBitRate_Min_Raw=DBL_MAX;
1151 float64 TimeStamp_InstantaneousBitRate_Max_Raw=0;
1152 int64u TimeStamp_Distance_Min=(int64u)-1;
1153 int64u TimeStamp_Distance_Max=0;
1154 int64u TimeStamp_Distance_Total=0;
1155 int64u TimeStamp_Distance_Count=0;
1156 int64u TimeStamp_HasProblems=0;
1157 #endif // MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED
1158
1159 int64u Duration_Count=0;
1160 int64u Duration_Max=0;
1161 int64u Duration_Sum=0;
1162 int64u Bytes_Sum=0;
1163 for (std::map<int16u, int16u>::iterator PCR_PID=Complete_Stream->PCR_PIDs.begin(); PCR_PID!=Complete_Stream->PCR_PIDs.end(); ++PCR_PID)
1164 {
1165 complete_stream::streams::iterator Stream=Complete_Stream->Streams.begin()+PCR_PID->first;
1166 if (*Stream && (*Stream)->TimeStamp_End_IsUpdated)
1167 {
1168 if ((*Stream)->TimeStamp_End<0x100000000LL*300 && (*Stream)->TimeStamp_Start>0x100000000LL*300)
1169 (*Stream)->TimeStamp_End+=0x200000000LL*300; //33 bits, cyclic
1170 if ((*Stream)->TimeStamp_Start<(*Stream)->TimeStamp_End)
1171 {
1172 int64u Duration=0;
1173 int64u Bytes=0;
1174 #if MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED
1175 if (Config->ParseSpeed>=1 && !(*Stream)->TimeStamp_Intermediate.empty())
1176 {
1177 Duration=(*Stream)->TimeStamp_Intermediate[0]-(*Stream)->TimeStamp_Start;
1178 size_t Last=(*Stream)->TimeStamp_Intermediate.size()-1;
1179 for (size_t Pos=1; Pos+1<Last; Pos+=2)
1180 Duration+=(*Stream)->TimeStamp_Intermediate[Pos+1]-(*Stream)->TimeStamp_Intermediate[Pos];
1181 Duration+=(*Stream)->TimeStamp_End-(*Stream)->TimeStamp_Intermediate[Last];
1182 }
1183 else
1184 #endif // MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED
1185 {
1186 Duration=(*Stream)->TimeStamp_End-(*Stream)->TimeStamp_Start;
1187 }
1188 Bytes=(*Stream)->TimeStamp_End_Offset-(*Stream)->TimeStamp_Start_Offset;
1189
1190 if (Duration>Duration_Max)
1191 Duration_Max=Duration;
1192 Duration_Count++;
1193 Duration_Sum+=Duration;
1194 Bytes_Sum+=Bytes;
1195
1196 (*Stream)->TimeStamp_End_IsUpdated=false;
1197 (*Stream)->IsPCR_Duration=(float64)Duration;
1198
1199 //Filling menu duration
1200 if (Count_Get(Stream_Menu))
1201 {
1202 complete_stream::transport_streams::iterator Transport_Stream=Complete_Stream->transport_stream_id_IsValid?Complete_Stream->Transport_Streams.find(Complete_Stream->transport_stream_id):Complete_Stream->Transport_Streams.end();
1203 if (Transport_Stream!=Complete_Stream->Transport_Streams.end())
1204 {
1205 //Per program
1206 for (size_t Pos=0; Pos<(*Stream)->program_numbers.size(); Pos++)
1207 {
1208 int16u program_number=(*Stream)->program_numbers[Pos];
1209 if (Transport_Stream->second.Programs[program_number].IsRegistered) //Only if the menu is already displayed
1210 Fill(Stream_Menu, Transport_Stream->second.Programs[program_number].StreamPos, Menu_Duration, ((float64)Duration)/27000, 6, true);
1211 }
1212 }
1213 }
1214 }
1215
1216 if ((*Stream)->TimeStamp_InstantaneousBitRate_BitRateMode_IsVbr>=Config_VbrDetection_Occurences)
1217 IsVbr=true;
1218 if ((*Stream)->TimeStamp_InstantaneousBitRate_BitRateMode_IsCbr)
1219 IsCbr=true;
1220 #if MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED
1221 if (Config->ParseSpeed>=1)
1222 {
1223 if (TimeStamp_InstantaneousBitRate_Min_Raw>(*Stream)->TimeStamp_InstantaneousBitRate_Min_Raw)
1224 TimeStamp_InstantaneousBitRate_Min_Raw=(*Stream)->TimeStamp_InstantaneousBitRate_Min_Raw;
1225 if (TimeStamp_InstantaneousBitRate_Max_Raw<(*Stream)->TimeStamp_InstantaneousBitRate_Max_Raw)
1226 TimeStamp_InstantaneousBitRate_Max_Raw=(*Stream)->TimeStamp_InstantaneousBitRate_Max_Raw;
1227 TimeStamp_Distance_Total+=(*Stream)->TimeStamp_Distance_Total;
1228 TimeStamp_Distance_Count+=(*Stream)->TimeStamp_Distance_Count;
1229 if (TimeStamp_Distance_Min>(*Stream)->TimeStamp_Distance_Min)
1230 TimeStamp_Distance_Min=(*Stream)->TimeStamp_Distance_Min;
1231 if (TimeStamp_Distance_Max<(*Stream)->TimeStamp_Distance_Max)
1232 TimeStamp_Distance_Max=(*Stream)->TimeStamp_Distance_Max;
1233 TimeStamp_HasProblems+=(*Stream)->TimeStamp_HasProblems;
1234 }
1235 #endif // MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED
1236 }
1237 }
1238
1239 if (Duration_Max)
1240 Fill(Stream_General, 0, General_Duration, ((float64)Duration_Max) / 27000, 6, true);
1241 if (Duration_Count && Duration_Sum && Bytes_Sum)
1242 {
1243 //Filling Duration and bitrate with an average of content from all streams with PCR
1244 //Min and Max are based on a a 1 byte precision in the computed byte count + +/- 500 ns tolerance for hte PCR vale
1245 Fill(Stream_General, 0, General_OverallBitRate, Bytes_Sum * 8 / (((float64)Duration_Sum) / 27000000), 0, true);
1246 Fill(Stream_General, 0, "OverallBitRate_Precision_Min", (Bytes_Sum - Duration_Count) * 8 / (((float64)(Duration_Sum + 13500 * Duration_Count)) / 27000000), 0, true);
1247 (*Stream_More)[Stream_General][0](Ztring().From_Local("OverallBitRate_Precision_Min"), Info_Options) = __T("N NT");
1248 Fill(Stream_General, 0, "OverallBitRate_Precision_Max", (Bytes_Sum + Duration_Count) * 8 / (((float64)(Duration_Sum - 13500 * Duration_Count)) / 27000000), 0, true);
1249 (*Stream_More)[Stream_General][0](Ztring().From_Local("OverallBitRate_Precision_Max"), Info_Options) = __T("N NT");
1250 }
1251
1252 if (IsVbr)
1253 Fill(Stream_General, 0, General_OverallBitRate_Mode, "VBR", Unlimited, true, true);
1254 else if (IsCbr)
1255 Fill(Stream_General, 0, General_OverallBitRate_Mode, "CBR", Unlimited, true, true);
1256 else
1257 Clear(Stream_General, 0, General_OverallBitRate_Mode);
1258 #if MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED
1259 if (Config->ParseSpeed>=1)
1260 {
1261 if ((IsVbr || !IsCbr) && TimeStamp_InstantaneousBitRate_Min_Raw<DBL_MAX)
1262 Fill(Stream_General, 0, General_OverallBitRate_Minimum, TimeStamp_InstantaneousBitRate_Min_Raw, 0, true);
1263 else
1264 Clear(Stream_General, 0, General_OverallBitRate_Minimum);
1265 if ((IsVbr || !IsCbr) && TimeStamp_InstantaneousBitRate_Max_Raw)
1266 Fill(Stream_General, 0, General_OverallBitRate_Maximum, TimeStamp_InstantaneousBitRate_Max_Raw, 0, true);
1267 else
1268 Clear(Stream_General, 0, General_OverallBitRate_Maximum);
1269 if (TimeStamp_Distance_Count)
1270 {
1271 Fill(Stream_General, 0, "PCR_Distance_Average", ((float64)TimeStamp_Distance_Total)/27000000/TimeStamp_Distance_Count, 9, true);
1272 (*Stream_More)[Stream_General][0](Ztring().From_Local("PCR_Distance_Average"), Info_Options)=__T("N NT");
1273 }
1274 if (TimeStamp_Distance_Min!=(int64u)-1)
1275 {
1276 Fill(Stream_General, 0, "PCR_Distance_Min", ((float64)TimeStamp_Distance_Min)/27000000, 9, true);
1277 (*Stream_More)[Stream_General][0](Ztring().From_Local("PCR_Distance_Min"), Info_Options)=__T("N NT");
1278 }
1279 if (TimeStamp_Distance_Max)
1280 {
1281 Fill(Stream_General, 0, "PCR_Distance_Max", ((float64)TimeStamp_Distance_Max)/27000000, 9, true);
1282 (*Stream_More)[Stream_General][0](Ztring().From_Local("PCR_Distance_Max"), Info_Options)=__T("N NT");
1283 }
1284 {
1285 Fill(Stream_General, 0, "PCR_Invalid_Count", TimeStamp_HasProblems, 10, true);
1286 (*Stream_More)[Stream_General][0](Ztring().From_Local("PCR_Invalid_Count"), Info_Options)=__T("N NT");
1287 }
1288
1289 }
1290 #endif // MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED
1291}
1292#endif //MEDIAINFO_MPEGTS_PCR_YES

1305{
1306 //Per stream
1307 for (size_t StreamID=0; StreamID<0x2000; StreamID++)
1308 if (Complete_Stream->Streams[StreamID]->Parser)
1309 {
1310 if (!Complete_Stream->Streams[StreamID]->Parser->Status[IsFinished])
1311 {
1312 int64u File_Size_Temp=File_Size;
1313 File_Size=File_Offset+Buffer_Offset+Element_Offset;
1314 Open_Buffer_Continue(Complete_Stream->Streams[StreamID]->Parser, Buffer, 0, false);
1315 File_Size=File_Size_Temp;
1316 Finish(Complete_Stream->Streams[StreamID]->Parser);
1317 #if MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
1318 if (Config->Demux_EventWasSent)
1319 return;
1320 #endif //MEDIAINFO_DEMUX
1321 }
1322 }
1323
1324 #if MEDIAINFO_DUPLICATE
1325 File__Duplicate_Streams_Finish();
1326 #endif //MEDIAINFO_DUPLICATE
1327
1328 #if MEDIAINFO_IBICREATE
1329 if (!IsSub && Config_Ibi_Create)
1330 {
1331 for (ibi::streams::iterator IbiStream_Temp=Ibi.Streams.begin(); IbiStream_Temp!=Ibi.Streams.end(); ++IbiStream_Temp)
1332 {
1333 if (IbiStream_Temp->second && IbiStream_Temp->second->DtsFrequencyNumerator==1000000000 && IbiStream_Temp->second->DtsFrequencyDenominator==1)
1334 {
1335 bool IsOk=true;
1336 for (size_t Pos=0; Pos<IbiStream_Temp->second->Infos.size(); Pos++)
1337 if (!IbiStream_Temp->second->Infos[Pos].IsContinuous && Pos+1!=IbiStream_Temp->second->Infos.size())
1338 IsOk=false;
1339 if (IsOk) //Only is all items are continuous (partial IBI not yet supported)
1340 {
1341 IbiStream_Temp->second->DtsFrequencyNumerator=90000;
1342 for (size_t Pos=0; Pos<IbiStream_Temp->second->Infos.size(); Pos++)
1343 {
1344 int64u Temp=IbiStream_Temp->second->Infos[Pos].Dts*90/1000000;
1345 IbiStream_Temp->second->Infos[Pos].Dts=Temp;
1346 }
1347 }
1348 }
1349 }
1350 }
1351 #endif //MEDIAINFO_IBIUSAGE
1352}

1357
1358//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
1359bool File_MpegTs::Synchronize()
1360{
1361 //Synchronizing
1362 while ( Buffer_Offset+188*16+BDAV_Size*16+TSP_Size*16<=Buffer_Size
1363 && !(Buffer[Buffer_Offset+188* 0+BDAV_Size* 1+TSP_Size* 0]==0x47
1364 && Buffer[Buffer_Offset+188* 1+BDAV_Size* 2+TSP_Size* 1]==0x47
1365 && Buffer[Buffer_Offset+188* 2+BDAV_Size* 3+TSP_Size* 2]==0x47
1366 && Buffer[Buffer_Offset+188* 3+BDAV_Size* 4+TSP_Size* 3]==0x47
1367 && Buffer[Buffer_Offset+188* 4+BDAV_Size* 5+TSP_Size* 4]==0x47
1368 && Buffer[Buffer_Offset+188* 5+BDAV_Size* 6+TSP_Size* 5]==0x47
1369 && Buffer[Buffer_Offset+188* 6+BDAV_Size* 7+TSP_Size* 6]==0x47
1370 && Buffer[Buffer_Offset+188* 7+BDAV_Size* 8+TSP_Size* 7]==0x47
1371 && Buffer[Buffer_Offset+188* 8+BDAV_Size* 9+TSP_Size* 8]==0x47
1372 && Buffer[Buffer_Offset+188* 9+BDAV_Size*10+TSP_Size* 9]==0x47
1373 && Buffer[Buffer_Offset+188*10+BDAV_Size*11+TSP_Size*10]==0x47
1374 && Buffer[Buffer_Offset+188*11+BDAV_Size*12+TSP_Size*11]==0x47
1375 && Buffer[Buffer_Offset+188*12+BDAV_Size*13+TSP_Size*12]==0x47
1376 && Buffer[Buffer_Offset+188*13+BDAV_Size*14+TSP_Size*13]==0x47
1377 && Buffer[Buffer_Offset+188*14+BDAV_Size*15+TSP_Size*14]==0x47
1378 && Buffer[Buffer_Offset+188*15+BDAV_Size*16+TSP_Size*15]==0x47))
1379 {
1380 Buffer_Offset++;
1381 while ( Buffer_Offset+BDAV_Size+1<=Buffer_Size
1382 && Buffer[Buffer_Offset+BDAV_Size]!=0x47)
1383 Buffer_Offset++;
1384 }
1385
1386 if (Buffer_Offset+188*16+BDAV_Size*16+TSP_Size*16>=Buffer_Size
1387 #ifdef MEDIAINFO_ARIBSTDB24B37_YES
1388 && !FromAribStdB24B37
1389 #endif
1390 )
1391 return false;
1392
1393 //Synched is OK
1394 if (!Status[IsAccepted])
1395 {
1396 Accept();
1397 }
1398 return true;
1399}
1400
1401//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
1402bool File_MpegTs::Synched_Test()
1403{
1404 while (Buffer_Offset+TS_Size<=Buffer_Size)
1405 {
1406 //Synchro testing
1407 if (Buffer[Buffer_Offset+BDAV_Size]!=0x47)
1408 {
1409 Synched=false;
1410 #if MEDIAINFO_DUPLICATE
1411 if (File__Duplicate_Get())
1412 Trusted++; //We don't want to stop parsing if duplication is requested, TS is not a lot stable, normal...
1413 #endif //MEDIAINFO_DUPLICATE
1414 return true;
1415 }
1416
1417 //Getting pid
1418 pid=(Buffer[Buffer_Offset+BDAV_Size+1]&0x1F)<<8
1419 | Buffer[Buffer_Offset+BDAV_Size+2];
1420
1421 complete_stream::stream* Stream=Complete_Stream->Streams[pid];
1422 if (Stream->Searching)
1423 {
1424 //Trace config
1425 #if MEDIAINFO_TRACE
1426 if (Config_Trace_Level)
1427 {
1428 if (Stream->Kind==complete_stream::stream::pes)
1429 {
1430 if (!Trace_Layers[8])
1431 Trace_Layers_Update(8); //Stream
1432 }
1433 else
1434 Trace_Layers_Update(IsSub?1:0);
1435 }
1436 #endif //MEDIAINFO_TRACE
1437
1438 payload_unit_start_indicator=(Buffer[Buffer_Offset+BDAV_Size+1]&0x40)!=0;
1439 if (payload_unit_start_indicator)
1440 {
1441 //Searching start
1442 if (Stream->Searching_Payload_Start) //payload_unit_start_indicator
1443 {
1444 if (Stream->Kind==complete_stream::stream::psi)
1445 {
1446 //Searching table_id
1447 size_t Version_Pos=BDAV_Size
1448 +4 //standart header
1449 +((Buffer[Buffer_Offset+BDAV_Size+3]&0x20)?(1+Buffer[Buffer_Offset+BDAV_Size+4]):0); //adaptation_field_control (adaptation) --> adaptation_field_length
1450 if (Version_Pos>=BDAV_Size+188)
1451 return true; //There is a problem with this block, accelerated parsing disabled
1452 Version_Pos+=1+Buffer[Buffer_Offset+Version_Pos]; //pointer_field
1453 if (Version_Pos>=BDAV_Size+188)
1454 return true; //There is a problem with this block, accelerated parsing disabled
1455 int8u table_id=Buffer[Buffer_Offset+Version_Pos]; //table_id
1456 #if MEDIAINFO_TRACE
1457 if (Trace_Activated)
1458 Stream->Element_Info1=Mpeg_Psi_table_id(table_id);
1459 #endif //MEDIAINFO_TRACE
1460 if (table_id==0xCD) //specifc case for ATSC STT
1461 {
1462 if (Config_Trace_TimeSection_OnlyFirstOccurrence)
1463 {
1464 if (!TimeSection_FirstOccurrenceParsed)
1465 TimeSection_FirstOccurrenceParsed=true;
1466 #if MEDIAINFO_TRACE
1467 else
1468 {
1469 Trace_Layers.reset(); //We do not want to display data about other occurences
1470 Trace_Layers_Update();
1471 }
1472 #endif //MEDIAINFO_TRACE
1473 }
1474 return true; //Version has no meaning
1475 }
1476 #if MEDIAINFO_IBIUSAGE
1477 if (table_id==0x00)
1478 Complete_Stream->Streams[pid]->Ibi_SynchronizationOffset_BeginOfFrame=File_Offset+Buffer_Offset;
1479 if (table_id==0x02)
1480 Complete_Stream->Streams[pid]->Ibi_SynchronizationOffset_BeginOfFrame=Complete_Stream->Streams[0x0000]->Ibi_SynchronizationOffset_BeginOfFrame;
1481 #endif //MEDIAINFO_IBIUSAGE
1482 complete_stream::stream::table_ids::iterator Table_ID=Stream->Table_IDs.begin()+table_id;
1483 if (*Table_ID)
1484 {
1485 //Searching table_id_extension, version_number, section_number
1486 if (!(Buffer[Buffer_Offset+Version_Pos+1]&0x80)) //section_syntax_indicator
1487 {
1488 if (table_id==0x70 && Config_Trace_TimeSection_OnlyFirstOccurrence)
1489 {
1490 if (!TimeSection_FirstOccurrenceParsed)
1491 TimeSection_FirstOccurrenceParsed=true;
1492 #if MEDIAINFO_TRACE
1493 else
1494 {
1495 Trace_Layers.reset(); //We do not want to display data about other occurences
1496 Trace_Layers_Update();
1497 }
1498 #endif //MEDIAINFO_TRACE
1499 }
1500 return true; //No version
1501 }
1502 Version_Pos+=3; //Header size
1503 if (Version_Pos+5>=BDAV_Size+188)
1504 return true; //Not able to detect version (too far)
1505 int16u table_id_extension=(Buffer[Buffer_Offset+Version_Pos]<<8)|Buffer[Buffer_Offset+Version_Pos+1];
1506 int8u version_number=(Buffer[Buffer_Offset+Version_Pos+2]&0x3F)>>1;
1507 int8u section_number=Buffer[Buffer_Offset+Version_Pos+3];
1508 complete_stream::stream::table_id::table_id_extensions::iterator Table_ID_Extension=(*Table_ID)->Table_ID_Extensions.find(table_id_extension);
1509 if (Table_ID_Extension==(*Table_ID)->Table_ID_Extensions.end())
1510 {
1511 if ((*Table_ID)->Table_ID_Extensions_CanAdd)
1512 {
1513 (*Table_ID)->Table_ID_Extensions[table_id_extension].version_number=version_number;
1514 (*Table_ID)->Table_ID_Extensions[table_id_extension].Section_Numbers.resize(0x100);
1515 (*Table_ID)->Table_ID_Extensions[table_id_extension].Section_Numbers[section_number]=true;
1516 return true; //table_id_extension is not yet parsed
1517 }
1518 }
1519 else if (Table_ID_Extension->second.version_number!=version_number)
1520 {
1521 if (Table_ID_Extension->second.version_number!=(int8u)-1 && Config_Trace_TimeSection_OnlyFirstOccurrence)
1522 break;
1523 Table_ID_Extension->second.version_number=version_number;
1524 Table_ID_Extension->second.Section_Numbers.clear();
1525 Table_ID_Extension->second.Section_Numbers.resize(0x100);
1526 Table_ID_Extension->second.Section_Numbers[section_number]=true;
1527 return true; //version is different
1528 }
1529 else if (!Table_ID_Extension->second.Section_Numbers[section_number])
1530 {
1531 Table_ID_Extension->second.Section_Numbers[section_number]=true;
1532 return true; //section is not yet parsed
1533 }
1534 else if (table_id==0x02 && Complete_Stream->Transport_Streams[Complete_Stream->transport_stream_id].Programs_NotParsedCount)
1535 {
1536 //PMT is looping, so this is nearly sure that all PMT available in the stream are assigned
1537 #ifdef MEDIAINFO_MPEGTS_ALLSTREAMS_YES
1538 for (size_t pid=0x10; pid<0x1FFF; pid++) //Wanting 0x10-->0x2F (DVB), 0x1ABC (cea_osd), 0x1FF7-->0x1FFF (ATSC)
1539 for (size_t Table_ID=0x00; Table_ID<0xFF; Table_ID++)
1540 {
1541 Complete_Stream->Streams[pid]->Searching_Payload_Start_Set(true);
1542 Complete_Stream->Streams[pid]->Kind=complete_stream::stream::psi;
1543 Complete_Stream->Streams[pid]->Table_IDs.resize(0x100);
1544 Complete_Stream->Streams[pid]->Table_IDs[Table_ID]=new complete_stream::stream::table_id; //event_information_section - actual_transport_stream, schedule
1545
1546 if (Pos==0x001F)
1547 Pos=0x1ABB; //Skipping normal data
1548 if (Pos==0x01ABC)
1549 Pos=0x1FF6; //Skipping normal data
1550 }
1551 #else //MEDIAINFO_MPEGTS_ALLSTREAMS_YES
1552 if (Complete_Stream->Streams[0x0010]->Kind==complete_stream::stream::unknown)
1553 {
1554 Complete_Stream->Streams[0x0010]->Searching_Payload_Start_Set(true);
1555 Complete_Stream->Streams[0x0010]->Kind=complete_stream::stream::psi;
1556 Complete_Stream->Streams[0x0010]->Table_IDs.resize(0x100);
1557 Complete_Stream->Streams[0x0010]->Table_IDs[0x40]=new complete_stream::stream::table_id; //network_information_section - actual_network
1558 }
1559 if (Complete_Stream->Streams[0x0011]->Kind==complete_stream::stream::unknown)
1560 {
1561 Complete_Stream->Streams[0x0011]->Searching_Payload_Start_Set(true);
1562 Complete_Stream->Streams[0x0011]->Kind=complete_stream::stream::psi;
1563 Complete_Stream->Streams[0x0011]->Table_IDs.resize(0x100);
1564 Complete_Stream->Streams[0x0011]->Table_IDs[0x42]=new complete_stream::stream::table_id; //service_description_section - actual_transport_stream
1565 }
1566 if (Complete_Stream->Streams[0x0012]->Kind==complete_stream::stream::unknown)
1567 {
1568 Complete_Stream->Streams[0x0012]->Searching_Payload_Start_Set(true);
1569 Complete_Stream->Streams[0x0012]->Kind=complete_stream::stream::psi;
1570 Complete_Stream->Streams[0x0012]->Table_IDs.resize(0x100);
1571 Complete_Stream->Streams[0x0012]->Table_IDs[0x4E]=new complete_stream::stream::table_id; //event_information_section - actual_transport_stream, present/following
1572 for (size_t Table_ID=0x50; Table_ID<0x60; Table_ID++)
1573 Complete_Stream->Streams[0x0012]->Table_IDs[Table_ID]=new complete_stream::stream::table_id; //event_information_section - actual_transport_stream, schedule
1574 }
1575 if (Complete_Stream->Streams[0x0014]->Kind==complete_stream::stream::unknown)
1576 {
1577 Complete_Stream->Streams[0x0014]->Searching_Payload_Start_Set(true);
1578 Complete_Stream->Streams[0x0014]->Kind=complete_stream::stream::psi;
1579 Complete_Stream->Streams[0x0014]->Table_IDs.resize(0x100);
1580 Complete_Stream->Streams[0x0014]->Table_IDs[0x70]=new complete_stream::stream::table_id; //time_date_section
1581 Complete_Stream->Streams[0x0014]->Table_IDs[0x73]=new complete_stream::stream::table_id; //time_offset_section
1582 }
1583 if (Complete_Stream->Streams[0x1FFB]->Kind==complete_stream::stream::unknown)
1584 {
1585 Complete_Stream->Streams[0x1FFB]->Searching_Payload_Start_Set(true);
1586 Complete_Stream->Streams[0x1FFB]->Kind=complete_stream::stream::psi;
1587 Complete_Stream->Streams[0x1FFB]->Table_IDs.resize(0x100);
1588 Complete_Stream->Streams[0x1FFB]->Table_IDs[0xC7]=new complete_stream::stream::table_id; //Master Guide Table
1589 Complete_Stream->Streams[0x1FFB]->Table_IDs[0xCD]=new complete_stream::stream::table_id; //System Time Table
1590 }
1591 #endif //MEDIAINFO_MPEGTS_ALLSTREAMS_YES
1592 }
1593 }
1594 }
1595 else
1596 return true; //No version in this pid
1597 }
1598 }
1599
1600 //Searching continue and parser timestamp
1601 if (Stream->Searching_Payload_Continue
1602 #ifdef MEDIAINFO_MPEGTS_PESTIMESTAMP_YES
1603 || Stream->Searching_ParserTimeStamp_Start
1604 || Stream->Searching_ParserTimeStamp_End
1605 #endif //MEDIAINFO_MPEGTS_PESTIMESTAMP_YES
1606 )
1607 return true;
1608
1609 //Adaptation layer
1610 #ifdef MEDIAINFO_MPEGTS_PCR_YES
1611 if (( Stream->Searching_TimeStamp_Start
1612 || Stream->Searching_TimeStamp_End)
1613 #ifdef MEDIAINFO_MPEGTS_PESTIMESTAMP_YES
1614 && !Stream->Searching_ParserTimeStamp_End
1615 #endif //MEDIAINFO_MPEGTS_PESTIMESTAMP_YES
1616 )
1617 {
1618 if ((Buffer[Buffer_Offset+BDAV_Size+3]&0x20)==0x20) //adaptation_field_control (adaptation)
1619 {
1620 int8u adaptation_field_length=Buffer[Buffer_Offset+BDAV_Size+4];
1621 if (adaptation_field_length>=5) //adaptation_field_length
1622 {
1623 bool discontinuity_indicator=(Buffer[Buffer_Offset+BDAV_Size+5]&0x80)!=0;
1624 bool PCR_flag=(Buffer[Buffer_Offset+BDAV_Size+5]&0x10)!=0;
1625 if (PCR_flag)
1626 {
1627 int64u program_clock_reference=( (((int64u)Buffer[Buffer_Offset+BDAV_Size+6])<<25)
1628 | (((int64u)Buffer[Buffer_Offset+BDAV_Size+7])<<17)
1629 | (((int64u)Buffer[Buffer_Offset+BDAV_Size+8])<< 9)
1630 | (((int64u)Buffer[Buffer_Offset+BDAV_Size+9])<< 1)
1631 | (((int64u)Buffer[Buffer_Offset+BDAV_Size+10])>>7));
1632 program_clock_reference*=300;
1633 program_clock_reference+=( (((int64u)Buffer[Buffer_Offset+BDAV_Size+10]&0x01)<<8)
1634 | (((int64u)Buffer[Buffer_Offset+BDAV_Size+11]) ));
1635 if (Complete_Stream->Streams[pid]->Searching_TimeStamp_End
1636 #ifdef MEDIAINFO_MPEGTS_PESTIMESTAMP_YES
1637 && (!Complete_Stream->Streams[pid]->Searching_ParserTimeStamp_End
1638 || Complete_Stream->Streams[pid]->IsPCR) //If PCR, we always want it.
1639 #endif //MEDIAINFO_MPEGTS_PESTIMESTAMP_YES
1640 )
1641 {
1642 Header_Parse_Events_Duration(program_clock_reference);
1643 if (program_clock_reference!=Complete_Stream->Streams[pid]->TimeStamp_End) //Some PCRs are buggy (low precision), using the first stream offset in the case of duplicate PCR value
1644 {
1645 if (Complete_Stream->Streams[pid]->TimeStamp_End_Offset!=(int64u)-1)
1646 {
1647 if (program_clock_reference+0x12c00000000LL<Complete_Stream->Streams[pid]->TimeStamp_End)
1648 program_clock_reference+=0x25800000000LL; //33 bits and *300
1649 if (!discontinuity_indicator && program_clock_reference>Complete_Stream->Streams[pid]->TimeStamp_End && program_clock_reference<Complete_Stream->Streams[pid]->TimeStamp_End+10*27000000) //Not before, not after 10 seconds, else there is a problem
1650 {
1651 float64 Duration_InstantaneousBitRate_Min=(float64)(program_clock_reference-Complete_Stream->Streams[pid]->TimeStamp_End-(Config_VbrDetection_Delta?0:810));
1652 float64 Duration_InstantaneousBitRate_Max=(float64)(program_clock_reference-Complete_Stream->Streams[pid]->TimeStamp_End+(Config_VbrDetection_Delta?0:810));
1653 float64 Bytes_InstantaneousBitRate=(float64)(File_Offset+Buffer_Offset-Complete_Stream->Streams[pid]->TimeStamp_End_Offset);
1654 float64 TimeStamp_InstantaneousBitRate_Current_Min=Bytes_InstantaneousBitRate*8/Duration_InstantaneousBitRate_Max*27000000*(1-Config_VbrDetection_Delta);
1655 float64 TimeStamp_InstantaneousBitRate_Current_Raw=Bytes_InstantaneousBitRate*8/Duration_InstantaneousBitRate_Min*27000000;
1656 float64 TimeStamp_InstantaneousBitRate_Current_Max=Bytes_InstantaneousBitRate*8/Duration_InstantaneousBitRate_Min*27000000*(1+Config_VbrDetection_Delta);
1657 if (Complete_Stream->Streams[pid]->TimeStamp_InstantaneousBitRate_Current_Min)
1658 {
1659 if (TimeStamp_InstantaneousBitRate_Current_Max<Complete_Stream->Streams[pid]->TimeStamp_InstantaneousBitRate_Current_Min || TimeStamp_InstantaneousBitRate_Current_Min>Complete_Stream->Streams[pid]->TimeStamp_InstantaneousBitRate_Current_Max)
1660 {
1661 Complete_Stream->Streams[pid]->TimeStamp_InstantaneousBitRate_BitRateMode_IsVbr++;
1662 #if MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED
1663 if (Config_VbrDetection_GiveUp && Complete_Stream->Streams[pid]->TimeStamp_InstantaneousBitRate_BitRateMode_IsVbr>=Config_VbrDetection_Occurences)
1664 Config->ParseSpeed=0;
1665 #endif // MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED
1666 }
1667 else
1668 Complete_Stream->Streams[pid]->TimeStamp_InstantaneousBitRate_BitRateMode_IsCbr++;
1669 }
1670 float64 Duration_Min=(float64)(program_clock_reference-Complete_Stream->Streams[pid]->TimeStamp_End-1);
1671 float64 Duration_Raw=(float64)(program_clock_reference-Complete_Stream->Streams[pid]->TimeStamp_End);
1672 float64 Duration_Max=(float64)(program_clock_reference-Complete_Stream->Streams[pid]->TimeStamp_End+1);
1673 float64 Bytes=(float64)(File_Offset+Buffer_Offset-Complete_Stream->Streams[pid]->TimeStamp_End_Offset);
1674 float64 TimeStamp_Min=Bytes*8/Duration_Max*27000000*(1-Config_VbrDetection_Delta);
1675 float64 TimeStamp_Raw=Bytes*8/Duration_Raw*27000000;
1676 float64 TimeStamp_Max=Bytes*8/Duration_Min*27000000*(1+Config_VbrDetection_Delta);
1677 Complete_Stream->Streams[pid]->TimeStamp_InstantaneousBitRate_Current_Min=TimeStamp_Min;
1678 Complete_Stream->Streams[pid]->TimeStamp_InstantaneousBitRate_Current_Raw=TimeStamp_Raw;
1679 Complete_Stream->Streams[pid]->TimeStamp_InstantaneousBitRate_Current_Max=TimeStamp_Max;
1680 #if MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED
1681 if (Complete_Stream->Streams[pid]->TimeStamp_InstantaneousBitRate_Min_Raw>TimeStamp_InstantaneousBitRate_Current_Raw)
1682 Complete_Stream->Streams[pid]->TimeStamp_InstantaneousBitRate_Min_Raw=TimeStamp_InstantaneousBitRate_Current_Raw;
1683 if (Complete_Stream->Streams[pid]->TimeStamp_InstantaneousBitRate_Max_Raw<TimeStamp_InstantaneousBitRate_Current_Raw)
1684 Complete_Stream->Streams[pid]->TimeStamp_InstantaneousBitRate_Max_Raw=TimeStamp_InstantaneousBitRate_Current_Raw;
1685 int64u Distance=program_clock_reference-Complete_Stream->Streams[pid]->TimeStamp_End;
1686 if (Complete_Stream->Streams[pid]->TimeStamp_Distance_Min>Distance)
1687 Complete_Stream->Streams[pid]->TimeStamp_Distance_Min=Distance;
1688 if (Complete_Stream->Streams[pid]->TimeStamp_Distance_Max<Distance)
1689 Complete_Stream->Streams[pid]->TimeStamp_Distance_Max=Distance;
1690 Complete_Stream->Streams[pid]->TimeStamp_Distance_Total+=Distance;
1691 Complete_Stream->Streams[pid]->TimeStamp_Distance_Count++;
1692 #endif // MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED
1693 }
1694 #if MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED
1695 else
1696 {
1697 if (!discontinuity_indicator)
1698 Complete_Stream->Streams[pid]->TimeStamp_HasProblems++;
1699 float64 Bytes=(float64)(File_Offset+Buffer_Offset-Complete_Stream->Streams[pid]->TimeStamp_End_Offset);
1700 int64u TimeToAdd;
1701 if (Complete_Stream->Streams[pid]->TimeStamp_InstantaneousBitRate_Current_Raw)
1702 TimeToAdd=float64_int64s(Bytes*8/Complete_Stream->Streams[pid]->TimeStamp_InstantaneousBitRate_Current_Raw*27000000);
1703 else
1704 TimeToAdd=0;
1705 Complete_Stream->Streams[pid]->TimeStamp_Intermediate.push_back(Complete_Stream->Streams[pid]->TimeStamp_End+TimeToAdd);
1706 Complete_Stream->Streams[pid]->TimeStamp_Intermediate.push_back(program_clock_reference);
1707 }
1708 #endif // MEDIAINFO_ADVANCED
1709 }
1710 Complete_Stream->Streams[pid]->TimeStamp_End=program_clock_reference;
1711 Complete_Stream->Streams[pid]->TimeStamp_End_IsUpdated=true;
1712 Complete_Stream->Streams[pid]->TimeStamp_End_Offset=File_Offset+Buffer_Offset;
1713 {
1714 Status[IsUpdated]=true;
1715 Status[User_16]=true;
1716 }
1717 }
1718 }
1719 if (Complete_Stream->Streams[pid]->Searching_TimeStamp_Start)
1720 {
1721 //This is the first PCR
1722 Complete_Stream->Streams[pid]->TimeStamp_Start=program_clock_reference;
1723 Complete_Stream->Streams[pid]->TimeStamp_Start_Offset=File_Offset+Buffer_Offset;
1724 Complete_Stream->Streams[pid]->TimeStamp_End=program_clock_reference;
1725 Complete_Stream->Streams[pid]->TimeStamp_End_IsUpdated=true;
1726 Complete_Stream->Streams[pid]->TimeStamp_End_Offset=File_Offset+Buffer_Offset;
1727 Complete_Stream->Streams[pid]->Searching_TimeStamp_Start_Set(false);
1728 Complete_Stream->Streams[pid]->Searching_TimeStamp_End_Set(true);
1729 Complete_Stream->Streams_With_StartTimeStampCount++;
1730 {
1731 Status[IsUpdated]=true;
1732 Status[User_16]=true;
1733 }
1734 }
1735
1736 //Test if we can find the TS bitrate
1737 if (!Complete_Stream->Streams[pid]->EndTimeStampMoreThanxSeconds && Complete_Stream->Streams[pid]->TimeStamp_Start!=(int64u)-1
1738 && (File_Offset+Buffer_Offset-Buffer_TotalBytes_FirstSynched)*2<File_Size)
1739 {
1740 if (program_clock_reference<Complete_Stream->Streams[pid]->TimeStamp_Start)
1741 program_clock_reference+=0x200000000LL*300; //33 bits, cyclic
1742 if ((program_clock_reference-Complete_Stream->Streams[pid]->TimeStamp_Start)>Begin_MaxDuration)
1743 {
1744 Complete_Stream->Streams[pid]->EndTimeStampMoreThanxSeconds=true;
1745 Complete_Stream->Streams_With_EndTimeStampMoreThanxSecondsCount++;
1746 if (Complete_Stream->Streams_NotParsedCount
1747 && Complete_Stream->Streams_With_StartTimeStampCount>0
1748 && Complete_Stream->Streams_With_StartTimeStampCount==Complete_Stream->Streams_With_EndTimeStampMoreThanxSecondsCount)
1749 {
1750 //We are already parsing 16 seconds (for all PCRs), we don't hope to have more info
1751 MpegTs_JumpTo_Begin=File_Offset+Buffer_Offset-Buffer_TotalBytes_FirstSynched;
1752 MpegTs_JumpTo_End=MpegTs_JumpTo_Begin;
1753 if (MpegTs_JumpTo_Begin+MpegTs_JumpTo_End>=File_Size)
1754 {
1755 if (MpegTs_JumpTo_Begin+MpegTs_JumpTo_End>File_Size)
1756 {
1757 MpegTs_JumpTo_Begin=File_Size;
1758 MpegTs_JumpTo_End=0;
1759 }
1760 else
1761 MpegTs_JumpTo_Begin=File_Size-MpegTs_JumpTo_End;
1762 }
1763 }
1764 }
1765 }
1766 }
1767 }
1768 }
1769 }
1770 #endif //MEDIAINFO_MPEGTS_PCR_YES
1771 }
1772
1773 #if MEDIAINFO_DUPLICATE
1774 if (Stream->ShouldDuplicate)
1775 {
1776 Element_Size=TS_Size;
1777 File__Duplicate_Write();
1778 }
1779 #endif //MEDIAINFO_DUPLICATE
1780
1781 Header_Parse_Events();
1782
1783 Buffer_Offset+=TS_Size;
1784 }
1785
1786 if (File_Offset+Buffer_Size>=File_Size)
1787 Detect_EOF(); //for TRP files
1788
1789 return false; //Not enough data
1790}

1829 }
1830
1831 //Config
1832 Config_Trace_TimeSection_OnlyFirstOccurrence=MediaInfoLib::Config.Trace_TimeSection_OnlyFirstOccurrence_Get();
1833 TimeSection_FirstOccurrenceParsed=false;

1851 Option_Manage();
1852}

1858//---------------------------------------------------------------------------
1859void File_MpegTs::Read_Buffer_Unsynched()
1860{
1861 if (Complete_Stream==NULL || Complete_Stream->Streams.empty())
1862 return;
1863
1864 for (size_t StreamID=0; StreamID<0x2000; StreamID++)//std::map<int64u, stream>::iterator Stream=Streams.begin(); Stream!=Streams.end(); Stream++)
1865 {
1866 //End timestamp is out of date
1867 #if defined(MEDIAINFO_MPEGTS_PCR_YES) || defined(MEDIAINFO_MPEGTS_PESTIMESTAMP_YES)
1868 Complete_Stream->Streams[StreamID]->Searching_TimeStamp_Start_Set(false); //No more searching start
1869 Complete_Stream->Streams[StreamID]->TimeStamp_End=(int64u)-1;
1870 Complete_Stream->Streams[StreamID]->TimeStamp_End_IsUpdated=false;
1871 Complete_Stream->Streams[StreamID]->TimeStamp_End_Offset=(int64u)-1;
1872 if (Complete_Stream->Streams[StreamID]->TimeStamp_Start!=(int64u)-1)
1873 Complete_Stream->Streams[StreamID]->Searching_TimeStamp_End_Set(true); //Searching only for a start found
1874 #endif //defined(MEDIAINFO_MPEGTS_PCR_YES) || defined(MEDIAINFO_MPEGTS_PESTIMESTAMP_YES)
1875 if (Complete_Stream->Streams[StreamID]->Parser)
1876 {
1877 #ifdef MEDIAINFO_MPEGTS_PESTIMESTAMP_YES
1878 Complete_Stream->Streams[StreamID]->Searching_ParserTimeStamp_Start_Set(false); //No more searching start
1879 if (((File_MpegPs*)Complete_Stream->Streams[StreamID]->Parser)->HasTimeStamps)
1880 Complete_Stream->Streams[StreamID]->Searching_ParserTimeStamp_End_Set(true); //Searching only for a start found
1881 #endif //MEDIAINFO_MPEGTS_PESTIMESTAMP_YES
1882 if (File_GoTo==0)
1883 Complete_Stream->Streams[StreamID]->Parser->Unsynch_Frame_Count=0;
1884 Complete_Stream->Streams[StreamID]->Parser->Open_Buffer_Unsynch();
1885 }
1886 #if MEDIAINFO_IBIUSAGE
1887 Complete_Stream->Streams[StreamID]->Ibi_SynchronizationOffset_BeginOfFrame=(int64u)-1;
1888 for (complete_stream::stream::table_ids::iterator TableID=Complete_Stream->Streams[StreamID]->Table_IDs.begin(); TableID!=Complete_Stream->Streams[StreamID]->Table_IDs.end(); ++TableID)
1889 if (*TableID)
1890 for (complete_stream::stream::table_id::table_id_extensions::iterator TableIdExtension=(*TableID)->Table_ID_Extensions.begin(); TableIdExtension!=(*TableID)->Table_ID_Extensions.end(); ++TableIdExtension)
1891 TableIdExtension->second.version_number=(int8u)-1;
1892 #endif //MEDIAINFO_IBIUSAGE
1893 }
1894 Complete_Stream->Duration_End.clear();
1895
1896 //Clearing durations
1897 Clear(Stream_General, 0, General_Duration);
1898 Clear(Stream_General, 0, General_Duration_End);
1899 for (size_t StreamPos=0; StreamPos<Count_Get(Stream_Menu); StreamPos++)
1900 Clear(Stream_Menu, StreamPos, Menu_Duration);
1901}
